  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Klotski</title>

    <para>
      <application>klotski</application> is a
      is a clone of the <application>Klotski</application> game.
      The objective is to move the patterned block to the 
      area bordered by green markers. 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&klotski-download-http;"/>
